		"description": {
			"value": "<p><strong>Bonus Action</strong> - 30 ft. - 7th Level (Evocation) - VS</p><br><p><strong>[[/save CHA]]{Charisma Save}</strong></p><ul><li><p><strong>Failure:</strong> Affected creature suffers an effect based on its current hit points:</p><ul><li><p><strong>50 HP or fewer:</strong> &amp;reference[Deafened] for 1 minute.</p></li><li><p><strong>40 HP or fewer:</strong> &amp;reference[Deafened] and &amp;reference[Blinded] for 10 minutes.</p></li><li><p><strong>30 HP or fewer:</strong> &amp;reference[Blinded], &amp;reference[Deafened], and &amp;reference[Stunned] for 1 hour.</p></li><li><p><strong>20 HP or fewer:</strong> Killed instantly.</p></li><li><p>&amp;reference[Celestial], &amp;reference[Elemental], &amp;reference[Fey], or &amp;reference[Fiend] that fails its save is banished to its plane of origin (if not already there) and cannot return for 24 hours except by a <em>@UUID[Compendium.elkan5e.elkan5e-spells.Item.5e0swEflzMmSszQ0]{Wish}</em> spell.</p></li></ul></li><li><p><strong>Success:</strong> No effect.</p></li></ul>",
